modDescription:
Adds a [gun](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-weapons/) mod that will randomly set fire to zombies. Basically burning shaft mod but for ranged. Mod and Schematic can be found in loot and at traders.

**[Download](https://docs.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1IJH3WT06sYYbWOZ8XcL-rck4O_BTJUVG)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/20895-toads-modlets/).
